p: 22,23-Dihydro-5,8-epidioxystigmast-6-en-3-ol ( 25) was surrounded by Luffariella cf. variabilis, Tethya sp., and sea squirt Dendrodoa grossularia [ 82, 85, 86, 87, 88]. (3β,5α,8α)-Epidioxy-22,23-cyclopropacholest-6-en-3-ol ( 26) and (3β,5α,8α)-endoperoxy-23-demethylgorgost-6-en-3-ol ( 27) were discovered in soft corals Sinularia maxima , S. gibberosa and Sinularia sp. [ 89, 90].
